						               													<description>A mini-expansion for Piraten Kapern, released in a promo pack at the &amp;quot;Stadt, Land, Spielt&amp;quot;-Event in Germany and Austria.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This blister contains two sorts of special cards which can be added to the game. Each special card is available 4 times.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The function of the first special card, called &amp;quot;Nach dem Sturm&amp;quot; (&amp;quot;After the storm!), is: You are allowed to roll any amount of dice just 2 times. You are still not allowed to reroll any skulls, but even with more than 3 skulls on first roll, you are allowed to reroll. You are not allowed to go to Skull Island and only receive points for each diamond and each gold coin, but twice the amount.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The second card is &amp;quot;Frieden&amp;quot; (&amp;quot;Peace&amp;quot;): You have to end your turn without any sabre. If you succeed, you get double the points, else you get -1000 points for each sabre, you had rolled and no points for your other rolls. You are allowed to go to Skull Island, but even there you are not allowed to roll sabres.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
